@startuml
title 論理位置と見た目位置の分離

'top to bottom direction
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing true
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam defaultFontName Yu Gothic UI
skinparam defaultFontSize 18
skinparam rectangle {
  RoundCorner 24
  BorderColor black
  BackgroundColor #f7fbff
  FontColor black
}
skinparam ArrowColor black
skinparam ranksep 20
skinparam nodesep 20

rectangle "cell (x, y)" as Cell
rectangle "canMove /\nfindPath" as Logic
rectangle "world target\nposition" as WorldTarget
rectangle "animatePosition()" as AnimatePosition
rectangle "displayArea\nscroll" as DisplayArea

Cell --> WorldTarget
Cell --> Logic
Logic ..> DisplayArea : 同じ cell から計算
WorldTarget -down-> AnimatePosition
AnimatePosition -down-> DisplayArea

note top of Logic
論理層
end note

note top of WorldTarget
見た目層
end note
@enduml
